---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import marketmateLogo from "../../assets/marketmate_logo.png";
---

<Layout title="MarketMate">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/projects" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to projects</a>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mb-3">
      <img src={marketmateLogo.src} alt="MarketMate logo" class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain" />
      <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border text-[11px] border-amber-100 text-orange-600 bg-orange-50/60">Starting soon</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">MarketMate</h1>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4 mb-3 md:w-4/5">
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-800">
        <div class="font-semibold mb-1">In one line</div>
        Fresh food, every week, without the stress. Subscribe in the app, swap what you don’t want, pick up nearby.
      </div>
      <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-[12px] text-gray-700">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-2">We curate a balanced weekly box.</div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-2">Use swaps to make it yours.</div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-2">Pickup is quick and close.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-[11px] mb-2">
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Weekly boxes</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">COCO hub‑and‑spoke</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Pickup points</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Farmer analytics</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4" style="line-height: 2">
      MarketMate is a mobile app. It keeps the good parts of a farmers market (fresh, seasonal, local) and removes the hassle. We plan with farmers, you get a box that fits real life.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">The app at a glance</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Subscribe to a Small, Standard, or Family box</li>
            <li>See your weekly preview with recipe tips</li>
            <li>Swap 1–2 items (we suggest smart alternatives)</li>
            <li>Add pantry items (eggs, bread, milk, honey)</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Pick your hub and pickup time window</li>
            <li>Show your QR code and go — pickup takes seconds</li>
            <li>Pause, skip, or cancel anytime in the app</li>
            <li>Pay securely (Mobile Money, Card)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
          Built for people who love local food. Every box comes with a personalized card, farmer stories, and the exact hub where your food was packed.
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-gray-600">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50/70">Support local farms</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 bg-indigo-50/70">Know where it’s grown</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-amber-100 text-amber-700 bg-amber-50/70">Personalized recipes</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Why we exist</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Grocery chaos wastes time and food. We make it calm: curated, seasonal, and on time for people and producers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How the system works</h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 space-y-1">
            <li>Subscribe in the app — we curate your weekly box.</li>
            <li>The platform aggregates everything into one hub order (super efficient).</li>
            <li>Farmers harvest to plan — fewer surprises, less waste.</li>
            <li>Pickup at a nearby hub. No last‑mile drama or delays.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Your weekly flow</h3>
        <ol class="ms-5 list-decimal text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>Preview your box (with recipe tips) in the app.</li>
          <li>Use swaps for items you don’t want. Add pantry items.</li>
          <li>Pick up at your hub. Scan your QR code. Done.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Who gets what</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">For people</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 space-y-1">
              <li>One subscription. Fresh food, weekly.</li>
              <li>Swaps for picky days. Pantry add‑ons anytime.</li>
              <li>Pickup is quick — no queues, no chaos.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">For farmers</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 space-y-1">
              <li>Clear orders. Predictable cashflow.</li>
              <li>Simple SMS/USSD to confirm weekly quantities.</li>
              <li>We forecast demand so you can plan planting.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Tools we use</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>Customer mobile app: subscribe, swap, add pantry, QR pickup</li>
          <li>Farmer USSD/SMS: confirm weekly orders, get paid</li>
          <li>Hub dashboard: scan QR, assemble boxes, track handoffs</li>
          <li>Admin: plan menus, forecast demand, pay farmers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">What we are / What we’re not</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We’re a weekly hub system (fast pickup, lower costs), not door‑to‑door couriers (expensive, unreliable for fresh produce).
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Who it’s for</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[12px]">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Households</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Restaurants</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Caterers</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Schools</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Corporate canteens</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80">Partner with us</a>
        <a href="mailto:gideonad.codez@gmail.com?subject=MarketMate%20pilot&body=Hi%20Gideon%2C%0D%0A%0D%0AWe%27re%20interested%20in%20the%20MarketMate%20pilot.%20Here%27s%20who%20we%20are%3A%0D%0A-%20%0D%0A-%20%0D%0A%0D%0AOur%20location%3A%0D%0AOur%20volume%20range%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AThanks!" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">Join the pilot</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">FAQ</h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-3">
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Is MarketMate a mobile app?</div>
            <p>Yes. Download the app, subscribe to a box, manage swaps, and show your QR code at pickup.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">How do swaps work?</div>
            <p>You get 1–2 swap credits per week. Don’t want okra? Swap for a suggested alternative (like green beans). Swaps close a few days before pickup so farmers can harvest on time.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">What if I’m traveling?</div>
            <p>Pause or skip in the app anytime. No penalties.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Can I get delivery?</div>
            <p>We’re pickup‑first to keep food fresh and costs low. Hubs are nearby and fast. Delivery may come later for special cases.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">How do farmers use it?</div>
            <p>Farmers don’t need smartphones. They get simple USSD/SMS orders each week to confirm quantities and get paid on time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>


